{"tid":1682696,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"外交部：侮辱國旗案判200小時社會服務令 內地男塗中國必勝判監4周","createTime":"2019-10-30T08:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T02:29:36.000Z","uid":65371,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"61e43c23d9397e251f8c50aad9a113a80aac22c8","tid":1682696,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:13:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/393304404377707/posts/981406295567512/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F393304404377707%2Fposts%2F981406295567512%2F&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt3%2FBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=83d4a618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/393304404377707/posts/981406295567512/</a><br />\n<br />\n【香港侮辱國旗案宣判了】<br />\n<br />\n據香港媒體報道，9月22日，在沙田新城市廣場，有示威者拆下國旗塗黑及踐踏，再將國旗扔進垃圾桶內推落城門河。涉案人當晚被捕，被控一項侮辱國旗罪。<br />\n<br />\n此案昨日在沙田裁判法院宣判，涉案人被判200小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港特區《國旗及國徽條例》第七條「保護國旗、國徽」規定：「任何人公開及故意以焚燒、損毀、涂劃、玷污、踐踏等方式侮辱國旗或國徽，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處第5級罰款及監禁3年。」<br />\n<br />\n8月18日，一名來自中國內地的男子，在美國駐港澳總領事館大門噴塗「中國必勝」字樣（「勝」字未塗完）。兩天後，香港東區法院指控其犯刑事毀壞罪，判處監禁4周。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/QX2k09Ej2oaB1wPhu3omAQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FQX2k09Ej2oaB1wPhu3omAQ&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt3%2FBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=ff4687a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/QX2k09Ej2oaB1wPhu3omAQ</a><br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n<br />\n歡迎關注公署官方微信公眾號(帳號:fmcoprc)，希望為你提供豐富有益的資訊和便捷周到的服務。"},{"pid":"e520cb0362eb5d371786b693466dbe60e43fbbdb","tid":1682696,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:13:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLXe8W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLXe8W.jpg&h=d3761788&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b50de84b136d818f1986c577c993c7a62d6e24bb","tid":1682696,"uid":4574,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyT